CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW CRMVETAPALEAD AS SELECT aa.ETAPA as ETAPA,aa.IDXCRMETAPA as IDXCRMETAPA,aa.MOSTRARMOTIV as MOSTRARMOTIV,aa.ORDEN as ORDEN,aa.PORCENTAJE as PORCENTAJE,aa.IDCRMPIPELINE0 as IDCRMPIPELINE0,a.PIPELINE as PIPELINE FROM CRMETAPA aa
 INNER JOIN 
CRMPIPELINE a ON a.IDXCRMPIPELINE = aa.IDCRMPIPELINE0 WHERE   a.BAJA= false AND  UPPER (a.MODULO) LIKE upper('%CRMOPORTUNIDAD%')
 ORDER BY ORDEN Asc;
